room_title: Escape room "Escape The Final Act: The Houdini Experience" by Electric City Escape in Scranton

The problem is after you entered the stage door, it locked behind you. The auditorium doors are locked from the outside. Is someone playing a trick on you, or is this a setup? One of Houdiniâ€™s competitors maybe? You must find your way out before you become the final act, a true vanishing act! You have one hour to pull off the greatest escape ever!
